<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">How to use it</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">you need to set the percentage values in the DOM as inline styles. as well as the text strings visible to users, set the following attributes in the component code below:</p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li><code>aria-valuenow</code></li>
    <li><code>aria-valuetext</code></li>
    <li><code>clip-path: inset(0% X% 0% 0%);</code> but you must use 100 minus percent complete value</li>
    <li><code>-webkit-clip-path: inset(0% X% 0% 0%)</code> but you must use 100 minus percent complete value</li>

</ul>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">CSS/SCSS location</h2>
<p class="govuk-body">Heroku prototyping kit: <code>src/assets/scss/tfs/custom/ufs/_progress-bar.scss</code></p>


